2008-06-20
----------

1. Some Refactoring of code [courtesy Chu Yeow, thanks!]
2. `injour ls` now shows the latest status of each user on Injour [Idea courtesy Chu Yeow, thanks!]

Example:
alice$ ./bin/injour ls
bob (bob-imac.:43215) -> [20-Jun-2008 03:48 PM] Trying out the latest version of injour

3. `injour show bob` now accepts parameters to control the number of statuses that you want to see (by default shows 5)

Example:
alice$ ./bin/injour show bob 10
# Will display the last 10 statuses

3. Injour is now available on the browser and accepts parameters to alter the number of statuses on display.

Example:

http://bobs-imac.local:43215/?number=10


